Machine Error Injection Tools

soft-inj
============
1.mce-inject
		mce-inject allows to inject machine check errors on the 
		software level into a running Linux kernel.
		
		Load: 
			git://git.kernel.org/pub/scm/utils/cpu/mce/mce-inject.git
		See mce-inject README for more.

	
hw-inject
=============
1.EINJ
		EINJ provides a hardware error injection mechanism.	It need BIOS and
		kernel support.
		
		See documentation/acpi/apei/einj.txt for more.